{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Payment System",
    "description": "Colección para probar la API REST de SystemPayment.\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Create User\n2. Register Card (usa `userId` guardado automáticamente)\n3. Create Payment (usa `userId` y `cardId`)\n4. Get User Payments\n\nVariables de colección:\n- `baseUrl`: URL base de la API (default http://localhost:3000)\n- `userId`: UUID del usuario (se rellena al crear usuario)\n- `cardId`: UUID de la tarjeta (se rellena al registrar tarjeta)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "cardId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica que la API esté en funcionamiento."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', data.id);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Ana García\",\n  \"email\": \"ana.garcia@example.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un usuario.\n\nBody:\n- `nombre` (string, requerido)\n- `email` (string email único, requerido)\n\nGuarda automáticamente el `id` en la variable de colección `userId`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User Payments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/payments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}", "payments"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene el historial de pagos de un usuario.\n\nPath:\n- `id` — UUID del usuario (`{{userId}}`)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Cards",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Card",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('cardId', data.id);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"usuario_id\": \"{{userId}}\",\n  \"titular\": \"Ana García\",\n  \"numero_tarjeta\": \"4111111111111111\",\n  \"fecha_expiracion\": \"12/28\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/cards",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["cards"]
            },
            "description": "Registra una tarjeta ficticia asociada a un usuario.\n\nSolo se persisten titular, expiración y últimos 4 dígitos (PCI-DSS).\n\nBody:\n- `usuario_id` (UUID)\n- `titular` (string)\n- `numero_tarjeta` (13–19 dígitos; no se almacena completo)\n- `fecha_expiracion` (`YYYY-MM-DD`, `MM/YY` o `MM/YYYY`)\n\nGuarda automáticamente el `id` en la variable de colección `cardId`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Payments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"usuario_id\": \"{{userId}}\",\n  \"tarjeta_id\": \"{{cardId}}\",\n  \"monto\": 150.75\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/payments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["payments"]
            },
            "description": "Registra un pago.\n\nLa API consulta el microservicio Python (`POST /process-payment`), obtiene `APPROVED` o `REJECTED` (~80%/20%) y guarda el registro en PostgreSQL.\n\nBody:\n- `usuario_id` (UUID)\n- `tarjeta_id` (UUID; debe pertenecer al usuario)\n- `monto` (number > 0)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
